He's a baby!

10:50.250 --> 10:52.000
I saw him go in.

10:52.041 --> 10:54.834
Operation Broken Bathroom

10:52.041 --> 10:54.834
is a go.

10:58.583 --> 11:00.709
Oh, no!

11:05.667 --> 11:07.750
Eew! Gross!

11:09.667 --> 11:11.709
Shoot!

11:16.000 --> 11:18.125
Aaah!

11:20.000 --> 11:23.125
Aaah!

11:23.166 --> 11:25.959
Ohh-- aah!

11:28.208 --> 11:29.875
[breathing hard]

11:29.917 --> 11:31.625
What the--

11:34.083 --> 11:36.709
There's no such thing

11:34.083 --> 11:36.709
as bad luck.

11:36.750 --> 11:38.750
There's no such

11:36.750 --> 11:38.750
thing as bad luck.

11:42.041 --> 11:44.375
There is such a thing

11:42.041 --> 11:44.375
as bad luck.

11:46.208 --> 11:47.917
Help!

11:47.959 --> 11:50.125
Let me outta here!

11:50.166 --> 11:53.417
If the door handle's

11:50.166 --> 11:53.417
