11:56.250 --> 11:58.291
[loud thud,

11:56.250 --> 11:58.291
thumping]

12:02.875 --> 12:05.208
Bad luck is real!

12:07.125 --> 12:10.291
I thought you don't believe

12:07.125 --> 12:10.291
